  "detailed_description": "<h1>Wishlist our friends' new game:</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>Drift Phonk 666 is a risk-rewarding physics-based drifting game about collecting phonk tapes and escaping deadly saws. You will master the art of drifting, go through tons of obstacles and collect all the music tapes from hell so people hear how good 𝖒𝖚𝖘𝖎𝖈 sounds.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1591870/extras/8744d9c1ba2e0a783c5a2b7c37e0c268.poster.avif?t=1639281773\" width=640 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1591870/extras/8744d9c1ba2e0a783c5a2b7c37e0c268.webm?t=1639281773\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1591870/extras/8744d9c1ba2e0a783c5a2b7c37e0c268.mp4?t=1639281773\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>• Fast-paced gameplay.<br>• Funky car physics without brakes. <br>• Unique 𝖆𝖊𝖘𝖙𝖍𝖊𝖍𝖎𝖈. <br>• Minimalist artstyle.<br>• 30 handcrafted  hardcore levels.<br>• Original phonk and trap soundtrack.<br>• DRIIIIIIIIIIIIIIIFT.<br>• Phonkeram salam, ostalnim soboleznuyiu.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1591870/extras/2835bc976a86d20a45b7432158e21b4c.poster.avif?t=1639281773\" width=640 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1591870/extras/2835bc976a86d20a45b7432158e21b4c.webm?t=1639281773\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1591870/extras/2835bc976a86d20a45b7432158e21b4c.mp4?t=1639281773\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
